data.description: 2 br. 1 ba. on a large .31 acre dividable lot in beautiful  Shady Cove, Or.  Remodled kitchen with a large 88" x 38"  island, and convenient pantry. New roof and new paint inside in 2016. New dbl. pane vinyl windows and outside paint  in 2017. Master bedroom has walk through closet to second bedroom. 12 x 20 ft. covered deck. and Large fenced in backyard with a 16' x 21' dog pen .Backyard has been organic for 25 yrs. Good well for a large garden. A couple or so water feautres. 1 has a waterfall and one is a boat. Outbuildings include a 12 x 18 DIY greenhouse, 8x8 pump house, 480 sq. ft shop/garage with 220 and a small fenced yard. RV parking with a 24' wide X 60' long,  commercial driveway apron and lots of parking and room for toys. Natural gas to the corner of the house. There is a chicken yard with a small coop attached to the back of the shop.
data.whatILove: This home has had the same owners for 25 yrs and has not been a rental. Would make a great permaculture project.  About 1/4 mile to the Rogue River with world class salmon and steelhead fishing and minuets  to downtown.  Close to rafting, hiking, camping and loads of outdoor activities. 5 mins. to Shady Cove Park boat launch. 20 min. drive to Lost Creek Lake and Cole Rivers hatchery. 15 mins. to Eagle Point Wal-Mart, 30 mins. to Medford.
